metadata.name: Hoppy Holidays Froghodlers #1/100
metadata.description:
Dearest Frogholders,

We just wanted to express our sincere gratitude for your ongoing support. Your loyalty means the world to us and we are so grateful to have you as a part of our community. We are excited to see what the future holds and are looking forward to all the joys that 2023 brings. Thank you again for everything.

Ribbit Ribbit
